<div class="container">
  {{#strikers-row title="Predict & Win"}}
    <p>Upgrade your Originals cards by predicting a top performer from each of the 8 remaining matches.</p>
    <p>If you pick a forward or a midfielder, your card gets upgraded if your player scores one or more goals.</p>
    <p>If you pick a defender or a keeper, your card gets upgraded if his team keeps a clean sheet (min. 60 minutes played, excluding injury time).</p>
    <p>Every time a card gets upgraded, it receives a star. The same card can be upgraded up to 3 times.</p>
    <p>Your pick for a game can be modified until kickoff. Cards will be upgraded shortly after the match's conclusion.</p>
  {{/strikers-row}}
  <div class="row">
    {{#each model.games as |game|}}
      <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3">
        {{clickable-card-placeholder game=game myCards=model.myCards myPicks=model.myPicks submitClicked=(action "submitClicked")}}
      </div>
    {{/each}}
  </div>
</div>
